00:51:59.479 --> 00:52:05.479
with a variety of Microsoft tools like Excel and things like that. Power BI is way cheaper,

00:52:05.479 --> 00:52:10.840
but typically, more people have Tableau. If you're a Tableau shop, I wouldn't recommend

00:52:10.840 --> 00:52:16.840
a solution to a problem buying Tableau, buying Power BI licenses. Use the technology that you

00:52:16.840 --> 00:52:24.360
have. It's much more important to have people that understand the project.

00:52:24.360 --> 00:52:29.560
I think somebody with industry experience is a good person to lead, and then having a few folks

00:52:29.560 --> 00:52:35.399
that can wrangle data, build dashboards, create that foundation with one or two data scientists.

00:52:35.399 --> 00:52:41.159
