00:53:51.879 --> 00:53:55.719
going down the path that we needed to, or did we discover something new that we now need to take

00:53:55.719 --> 00:54:00.919
into account, and go back a few steps and retry some things. As long as you have that level of

00:54:00.919 --> 00:54:08.280
